Title: Breast cancer detection using ensembled model
TechStack: deep learning, Swin Transformer, EfficientNet, DenseNet
Description: Engineered an ensemble deep learning model (Swin Transformer, EfficientNet DenseNet) achieving 93.01% validation accuracy. Improved diagnostic precision and reduced false positives across medical imaging datasets.

Title: Hybrid approach for Deep Fake Detection
Description: Designed a hybrid model combining CNNs and RNNs to detect deepfakes by extracting spatial/temporal features, enhancing detection accuracy and robustness against manipulation.
